Lfg travel the #Multiverse with @FelineFiendz

Sauvage has all but mastered his eye abilities which allow him to travel the multivese and visit different NFT universes! He was seen the likes of of himself through countless projects including becoming an champion in the lands of @TheBlinkess, @CryptoRenya and @FreaklandMamma! Through his travels Sauvage has been able to create connections across collections and build a new budding community from the mix of a colorful bunch of artist and art enthusiast. Lasting relationships being build off the the desire to make sure artist are seen while challenging challenging @metaM00's ability to grow, adapt and learn to provide value to his supporters while developing the IP of @FelineFiendz #4224. 

Welcome to the #Multiverse as we journey and discover concepts like what is means to embrace other versions of ourselves and the unique abilities that come with each identity... Be careful tho, sometimes our other selfs are more power than the one we choose to present to the world, and it may try to take your spot... In this season Sauvage struggles with identity and what it means to be a 1/1 in a sea of variants fighting for the top position in the multiverse.

Join us for @AHMC_Platform's first mint and continue along this riveting story of discovery! @FelineFiendz #4224 is #SauvageUchiha once more!
